---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Zyntel Co. Limited builds operational intelligence software for healthcare and regulated industries in East Africa. Headquartered in Kampala, Uganda."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>

    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">Zyntel Co. Limited</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">Operational Intelligence<br />for East Africa.</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
      <div class="container prose">

        <div class="prose-section">
          <p class="lead">We build software that gives hospitals and regulated organisations the operational visibility they need to run well. Our flagship product, Kanta, tracks medical equipment, monitors lab performance, and helps hospital teams make better decisions — starting with Uganda, built for East Africa.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose-section">
          <h2>Where we operate</h2>
          <p>Headquartered in Kampala, Uganda. Building for East Africa.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose-section">
          <h2>What we believe</h2>
          <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>Precision over assumption</h3>
              <p>Hospitals deserve tools that tell them what is actually happening, not approximations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>Measured. Managed.</h3>
              <p>Our signature: <code>zyntel() =&gt; &#123; "measured.managed" &#125;</code>. If it is not measured, it cannot be managed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>Built for the real world</h3>
              <p>Works on a 2018 Android phone with intermittent internet. We build for the infrastructure that actually exists in East African hospitals.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose-section">
          <h2>The team</h2>
          <p>Founded by a team of three based in Kampala: a CEO responsible for product and commercial strategy, a CTO who owns the laboratory intelligence stack, and a COO who manages operations and finance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose-section contact-cta">
          <p>Have a question or want to see Kanta in action?</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .page-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 5rem 0 6rem;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
  }

  .prose {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .prose-section {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .prose-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .prose-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .prose-section p {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  code {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .contact-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-cta p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .contact-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
